    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We originally had a mapping where you provide `query: q` in urlSync, but found that it quickly lead to people needing more customisation, and at that point, they'd need to make changes to this statemapping, and it wouldn't fit anymore.\r\n\r\nI wonder if there's more some way to make these kind of customisations easier:\r\n\r\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/exciting-field-zmsn1?file=/src/app.js\r\n\r\nmaybe some function that does the looping / mapping for you (since it does get a little verbose), but then what if people want to map the values?",
