  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "As you mentioned, customization gets harder if people select this `singleIndexQ`. But those who want to customize would choose `simple` stateMapping or implement their own from the scratch.\r\n\r\nOn the example you showed looks like generating `instant_search%5Bq%5D=15&instant_search%5Bundefined%5D%5Bbrand%5D%5B0%5D=HP` as a full query string. That is too verbose, and I expect `q=15&refinementList%5Bbrand%5D%5B0%5D=HP` or `q=15`.",
