  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @tnir, thanks for the contribution!\r\n\r\nWe usually don't add an API if users don't show interest for it. We never received any requests regarding this compatibility layer for v2, I guess migrations guides are enough for most of the people. Therefore we're not going to embed this in InstantSearch itself.\r\n\r\nWe however suggest to share this idea in [our Discourse forum](https://discourse.algolia.com) where the community shares their InstantSearch implementations. It could be interesting to see how many people engage with such a post to possibly add this feature in InstantSearch later!",
